title: Marvel NOW! Week 49 10/23/2013
description:
I didn't see a collected torrent for last this past week's Marvel NOW! titles, so I thought I'd upload one. Included are:

Daredevil 032
FF 013
Indestructible Hulk 014
Infinity Heist 2 of 4
Infinity: The Hunt 3 of 4
Iron Man 017
Marvel NOW What?! 001 (of 1, I suppose)
Nova 009
Savage Wolverine 010
Secret Avengers 010
Superior Carnage 4 of 5
Superior Spider-Man Team Up 005
Thunderbolts 017
Uncanny Avengers 013
Venom 042 (the final issue?! Noooooooo!)
Wolverine and the X-Men 037
Young Avengers 011

If you like them and have the money, buy them and support your favorite writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. This is my first upload on tpb, so, sorry if it's not up to snuff. Thanks be to all the uploaders and scanners and seeders out there!
